    ORDER BY [b].[DateCreated] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[Id], [b0].[Price], CAST(0 AS bit) AS [c], [p].[Author], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Content], [p].[DateCreated], [p].[DateModified], [p].[Description], [p].[HomeFlag], [p].[HotFlag], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[Image], [p].[Name], [p].[OriginalPrice], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], CAST(0 AS bit) AS [c0], [p0].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [p0].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [p0].[Description] AS [Description0], [p0].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [p0].[HomeOrder], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[Image] AS [Image0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[ParentId], [p1].[Author] AS [Author0], [p1].[CategoryId] AS [CategoryId0], [p1].[Content] AS [Content0], [p1].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated1], [p1].[DateModified] AS [DateModified1], [p1].[Description] AS [Description1], [p1].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag1], [p1].[HotFlag] AS [HotFlag0], [p1].[Id] AS [Id2], [p1].[Image] AS [Image1], [p1].[Name] AS [Name1], [p1].[OriginalPrice] AS [OriginalPrice0], [p1].[Price] AS [Price1], [p1].[PromotionPrice], [p1].[Publisher], [p1].[SeoAlias], [p1].[SeoDescription], [p1].[SeoKeywords], [p1].[SeoPageTitle], [p1].[SortOrder], [p1].[Status], [p1].[Tags], [p1].[ViewCount], [p0].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [p0].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [p0].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [p0].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [p0].[SortOrder] AS [SortOrder0], [p0].[Status] AS [Status0], [p].[PromotionPrice] AS [PromotionPrice0], [p].[Publisher] AS [Publisher0], [p].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias1], [p].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription1], [p].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords1], [p].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle1], [p].[SortOrder] AS [SortOrder1], [p].[Status] AS [Status1], [p].[Tags] AS [Tags0], [p].[ViewCount] AS [ViewCount0], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p0] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p1] ON [p0].[Id] = [p1].[CategoryId]

""SELECT [t].[Author], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Content], [t].[DateCreated], [t].[DateModified], [t].[Description], [t].[HomeFlag], [t].[HotFlag], [t].[Id], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OriginalPrice], [t].[Price], CAST(0 AS bit), [p0].[DateCreated], [p0].[DateModified], [p0].[Description], [p0].[HomeFlag], [p0].[HomeOrder], [p0].[Id], [p0].[Image], [p0].[Name], [p0].[ParentId], [p1].[Author], [p1].[CategoryId], [p1].[Content], [p1].[DateCreated], [p1].[DateModified], [p1].[Description], [p1].[HomeFlag], [p1].[HotFlag], [p1].[Id], [p1].[Image], [p1].[Name], [p1].[OriginalPrice], [p1].[Price], [p1].[PromotionPrice], [p1].[Publisher], [p1].[SeoAlias], [p1].[SeoDescription], [p1].[SeoKeywords], [p1].[SeoPageTitle], [p1].[SortOrder], [p1].[Status], [p1].[Tags], [p1].[ViewCount], [p0].[SeoAlias], [p0].[SeoDescription], [p0].[SeoKeywords], [p0].[SeoPageTitle], [p0].[SortOrder], [p0].[Status], [t].[PromotionPrice], [t].[Publisher], [t].[SeoAlias], [t].[SeoDescription], [t].[SeoKeywords], [t].[SeoPageTitle], [t].[SortOrder], [t].[Status], [t].[Tags], [t].[ViewCount]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Author], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Content], [p].[DateCreated], [p].[DateModified], [p].[Description], [p].[HomeFlag], [p].[HotFlag], [p].[Image], [p].[Name], [p].[OriginalPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[PromotionPrice], [p].[Publisher], [p].[SeoAlias], [p].[SeoDescription], [p].[SeoKeywords], [p].[SeoPageTitle], [p].[SortOrder], [p].[Status], [p].[Tags], [p].[ViewCount]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[Status] = 1
    ORDER BY [p].[DateCreated] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY

    ORDER BY [p].[DateCreated] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Author], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Content], [p].[DateCreated], [p].[DateModified], [p].[Description], [p].[HomeFlag], [p].[HotFlag], [p].[Image], [p].[Name], [p].[OriginalPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[PromotionPrice], [p].[Publisher], [p].[SeoAlias], [p].[SeoDescription], [p].[SeoKeywords], [p].[SeoPageTitle], [p].[SortOrder], [p].[Status], [p].[Tags], [p].[ViewCount]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[Status] = 1) AND ([p].[HotFlag] = CAST(1 AS bit))
    ORDER BY [p].[DateCreated] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p0] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
